title: The Only Way to Success w/ Jay Papasan

description:
Episode 412 - Want to know the secret to success? In this episode I interview Jay Papasan, author of one of my top 3 favorite books "The ONE Thing." We go in very deep on questions that I had from the book and I think you will get massive value from this episode!
